# React / Next.js Patterns

- Functional components, React 19
- `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, browser APIs, interactivity)
- Tailwind CSS 4 for styling; use existing design tokens (primary, secondary)
- Path alias: `@/components/`, `@/lib/`, `@/config/`
- i18n via next-intl; messages in `translations/`
- Match existing component naming and file structure in `src/components/`
